<sect1 id="ROUNDUP">
  <!-- DNT-Start --><title>ROUNDUP</title><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para><emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->ROUNDUP<!-- DNT-End --><indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->ROUNDUP<!-- DNT-End --></primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->ROUNDUP<!-- DNT-End --> function</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis><emphasis>realvalue</emphasis><emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <para><informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <colspec colwidth="77.80pt" />

        <colspec colwidth="275.00pt" />

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis>realvalue</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry>The floating-point value to round.</entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->Return:<!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->ROUNDUP<!-- DNT-End --> returns a single integer value.</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable></para>

  <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->ROUNDUP<!-- DNT-End --> </emphasis>function returns the
  rounded integer of the <emphasis>realvalue</emphasis><indexterm>
      <primary>realvalue</primary>
    </indexterm> by rounding any decimal portion to the next larger integer
  value, regardless of sign.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

  <!-- DNT-Start --><programlisting>SomeRealValue := 3.14159;
INTEGER4 MyVal := ROUNDUP(SomeRealValue); // MyVal is 4

SomeRealValue := -3.9;
INTEGER4 MyVal := ROUNDUP(SomeRealValue); // MyVal is -4
</programlisting><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para>See Also: <link linkend="ROUND"><!-- DNT-Start -->ROUND<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="TRUNCATE"><!-- DNT-Start -->TRUNCATE<!-- DNT-End --></link></para>
</sect1>
